<item>
            <title>[SPARK-6408] JDBCRDD fails on where clause with string literal</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-6408</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The generated SQL query string is incorrect on filtering string literals.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;where foo=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;bar&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; results in &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;where foo=bar&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following snippet reproduce the bug:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;$ SPARK_CLASSPATH=h2-1.4.186.jar spark/bin/spark-shell

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; java.sql.DriverManager
val url = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;jdbc:h2:mem:testdb0&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Class&lt;/span&gt;.forName(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;org.h2.Driver&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
val conn = DriverManager.getConnection(url)
conn.prepareStatement(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;create schema test&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).executeUpdate()
conn.prepareStatement(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;create table test.people (name TEXT(32) NOT NULL, theid INTEGER NOT NULL)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).executeUpdate()
conn.prepareStatement(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;insert into test.people values (&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;fred&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, 1)&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).executeUpdate()
conn.commit()
sql(s&quot;&quot;&quot;
CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE foobar
USING org.apache.spark.sql.jdbc
OPTIONS (url &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;$url&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, dbtable &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;TEST.PEOPLE&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)
&quot;&quot;&quot;)
sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;select * from foobar where NAME=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;fred&apos;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).collect

15/03/19 06:34:38 ERROR Executor: Exception in task 0.0 in stage 1.0 (TID 1)
org.h2.jdbc.JdbcSQLException: Column &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;FRED&quot;&lt;/span&gt; not found; SQL statement:
SELECT NAME,THEID FROM TEST.PEOPLE WHERE NAME = fred [42122-186]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note that it is likely that other data types also have similar problem.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
